* Connecting to wifi

Create supplicant conf mgt.conf
@code bash
network={
        ssid="SSID HERE"
        scan_ssid=1
        key_mgmt=WPA-EAP
        eap=TTLS
        identity="domain\username HERE"
        anonymous_identity="anon"
        password="CRACKED PASSWORD HERE"
        phase2="auth=PAP"
}
@end
Connect via supplicant
@code bash
sudo wpa_supplicant -D nl80211 -i wlan1 -c mgt.conf
@end
On another terminal get an IP from DHCP server
@code bash
sudo dhclient wlan2 -v
@end
